# Supabase persistence (optional locally; set in Vercel for production).
# Without these, progress is stored in the browser's localStorage instead.
# Copy to .env.local and fill in from your Supabase project (Settings -> API).
# The anon key is public by design — row access is enforced by RLS, so it is safe to ship.
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
